FBIS3-18703 "drweu045_b_94005" FBIS-WEU-94-045 Document Type:Daily Report 8 Mar 1994 BENELUX Belgium Chile Confirms Purchase of 20 Mirage Planes LD0803120194 Brussels Radio Vlaanderen International in English 1000 GMT 8 Mar 94 LD0803120194 Brussels Radio Vlaanderen International Language: English Article Type:BFN [Text] Chile is to buy 20 Mirage fighter planes from Belgium. This was confirmed by the Chilean defense minister. The 20 planes will replace the Chilean British planes which date from the fifties. It's not known exactly how much the Chileans are paying for the planes, but an amount of three billion francs was mentioned earlier. The planes are up for sale as a result of the cutbacks in the Belgian Army. The planes were previously refurbished.
